headline: Is Carnival Stock Attractive After Recent Price Dip and Travel Industry Optimism?
summary: If you have ever wondered whether Carnival Corporation & is trading at a bargain or too pricey, you are in the right place. Let us take a closer look at the stock's true value. The share price has seen some action lately, dipping 6.3% over the past week and sliding 2.9% in the last month. However, it remains up a healthy 7.5% since the start of the year and 9.3% over the past 12 months.
